{"title":"塔里木之歌","authors":["赵力心"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":5,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔里木之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔河水，绿油油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百年来空自流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南北两岸好土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野草丛生成荒丘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地苍茫阴云暗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风沙蔽日牧人愁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然一夜东风起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日暖天晴现绿洲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔河水，水连天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金浪银花不见边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士决心建农场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄会师忆当年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸风光无限好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜似当年南泥湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振臂一呼春雷动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"命令戈壁变江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔河水，浪滔滔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄干劲冲云霄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河长江一步跨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手攀日月胆气豪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑将风雨作汗巾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"试将明月当灯照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖渠填土四十方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方见太阳伸懒腰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塔河水，水盈盈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福源远流不尽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南北两岸风景异，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗飘拂岁月新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车如流水马如龙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦似金山棉似银，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"场场队队传捷报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉花双百粮千斤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵力心"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}